title: Unreal 2 Multiplayer client
description:
What is the U2XMP Community Edition Installer

    Well, as some of you may know I&#039;ve been working on this for some time now but the first version is now complete. What it is is basically an all-in-one installer for U2XMP with several key additions:

        * Pre-patched to 7710
        * New master server support by default
        * Some of the more common maps installed
        * My new PID healthbars and the masterserver UI preinstalled
        * MapVote and Summoner mutators included.
        * Full un-install support

BIG THX EQ2 FOR MAKING THIS...
